                        <persName xml:lang="per" type="supplied" key="ark:/81055/vdc_100164656305.0x000001 viaf_107030610">شبستری، محمود ابن عبد الكريم</persName>
                     </author>
                     <title xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc" key="work_1364">Gulshan-i rāz</title>
                     <title xml:lang="per" key="work_1364">گلشن راز</title>
                     <note>
                        <p>Mas̲navī on the principles of Sufism written by Maḥmūd Shabistarī in response to questions from a correspondent in Khurasan, around 717/1317, identified as Mīr Fakhr al-Sādāt al-Ḥusaynī by the mystic, poet and hagiographer, Jāmī</p>
                        <p>Not dated</p>
                     </note>
                     <textLang mainLang="per">Persian</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem class="http://lccn.loc.gov/sh2002005579 http://lccn.loc.gov/sh85100085" n="2" xml:id="Uk_IO_Islamic_4392-item2">
