                     <note>
                        <p>Mas̲navī on ethics according to Sufism by the poet and mystic ʿAṭṭār Nayshāpūrī, master of the poet and mystic Rūmī Balkhī</p>
                        <p>Copious notes in Turkish on early folios</p>
                        <p>Not dated</p>
                     </note>
                     <textLang mainLang="per" otherLangs="tur">Persian &amp; Turkish</textLang>
